    <p id="Par54">On the other hand, in our simulation study, we did not incorporate any covariate. To further investigate the performances of the four point estimates and the four interval estimation methods with a covariate, here we conducted additional simulation studies by considering a covariate under HWE (i.e., <inline-formula id="IEq402"><alternatives><tex-math id="M739">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
