      <p id="Par59">Here, we recall the existing point estimate and the corresponding CI obtained by the Fieller’s method [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR30">30</xref>, <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR31">31</xref>]. The existing point estimate of <inline-formula id="IEq472"><alternatives><tex-math id="M889">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
