      <p id="Par61">Here, we propose a penalized point estimate and obtain its corresponding CI by the PF method [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR32">32</xref>]. Notice that if the denominator <inline-formula id="IEq500"><alternatives><tex-math id="M953">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
