				\begin{document}$$\lambda \rightarrow \infty$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M1038"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>λ</mml:mi><mml:mo stretchy="false">→</mml:mo><mml:mi>∞</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2022_4721_Article_IEq540.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, the width of the CI will tend to be 0 and the CP will also tend to be 0. So, we select <inline-formula id="IEq541"><alternatives><tex-math id="M1039">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
